MappedResourceSet<GuestKeyType,HostKeyType> - Class in github.lightningcreations.lcjei.resources
Defines a set of resources mapped from one key type, to annother.
MappedResourceSet(ResourceSet<HostKeyType>, ResourceKeyMapper<GuestKeyType, HostKeyType>) - Constructor for class github.lightningcreations.lcjei.resources.MappedResourceSet
Constructs a new MappedResourceSet with a given hostSet and a bidirectional key mapping function.
Neither hostSet or keyMapper may be null.
mapToGuest(HostKeyType) - Method in interface github.lightningcreations.lcjei.resources.ResourceKeyMapper
Returns the guest key that can be used with a MappedResourceSet to get the resource with hostKey.
This method MUST be equality preserving and a perfect inverse to {ResourceKeyMapper.mapToHost(Object).
mapToHost(GuestKeyType) - Method in interface github.lightningcreations.lcjei.resources.ResourceKeyMapper
Returns the host key that backs the guest key in a MappedResourceSet.
This method MUST be equality preserving and a perfect inverse to ResourceKeyMapper.mapToGuest(Object).
Failure to abide by this contract may have unexpected results.
The mapping function does not permit null inputs and MUST NOT return null.
